topic: No primary continuous story identified in cluster.
evaluation: Initial inspection revealed no distinct groups of articles meeting the minimum size requirement of three for a continuous, developmental, and synthesizable story. Two potential two-article groups were identified: one concerning the GP workforce crisis (Articles 3 & 5) and another on women's safety and sexual harassment (Articles 1 & 7). However, as neither met the 'size is below 3' criteria for adequacy, all articles are designated as noise.
